        About this item

        • The Complete Bundle - Our Essence Diffuser has a large capacity and uses state of the art wave diffusion technology to atomize essential oils for ultimate wellness. The Essence diffuser includes 7 ambient light modes with two intensity settings for 14 different light combinations. It also includes 4 timer settings and a convenient auto shutoff feature for low water levels. Essence is made of BPA free plastic with a beautiful printed wood grain design.
        • Ancient Therapies Delivered As Intended By Nature - Our essential oils are formulated using high quality plants sourced from various regions of the world, such as lavender from France and Tea Tree from Australia. Our modern heat-less diffuser delivers the therapeutic properties of these plant oils as nature intended by using modern ultrasonic waves to atomize the oils instead of burning them with heat.
        • 10 Essential Plant Oils - Our Top 10 essential oils include lavender, eucalyptus, tea tree, orange, peppermint, lemongrass, jasmine, nutmeg, clove, and spearmint oils. All oils are therapeutic grade come in amber 10ml jars to protect from sun degradation
        • No Additives or Fillers - Absolutely zero cheap additives or fillers are used in creating our oils. We use local harvest (when possible).It takes longer but is better for the environment and creates a better essential oil. We employ a variety of extraction processes such as steam distillation and cold press depending on plant harvested.
        • What's Included – 1 ultrasonic essence diffuser, 10ml lavender essential oil, 10ml eucalyptus essential oil, 10ml tea tree essential oil, 10ml orange essential oil, 10ml peppermint essential oil, 10ml lemongrass essential oil, 10ml jasmine essential oil, 10ml nutmeg essential oil, 10ml clove essential oil, 10ml spearmint essential oil, power cable, and manual.

        How customer reviews and ratings work

        Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

        To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

        Relaxing but not quiet
        One of my favorite purchases ever! Been using this diffuser in my office for a couple weeks now, and it is the best thing ever! My mood and productivity have improved tremendously because of it. I leave my office door open when I am not in a meeting and one of my coworkers came in smelled the room, and gave me money to by her one for her home. Safe to say I will recommend this to anyone and everyone.I will say this is not a quiet diffuser. You will hear the water trickling/bubbling. It's relaxing, but if you want silence - this diffuser is not the one for you. Also the LED light is only on the thin band that separates the 2 parts, hardly noticeable if your room is lit up.

        Ariel
        5.0 out of 5 stars Just what I was looking for!
        Reviewed in the United States on December 30, 2023
        Color: Wood GrainVerified Purchase
        I bought this product because I love aromatherapy and I wanted to have a diffuser that can match my home decor. I was impressed by the design and quality of this diffuser. It has a sleek and elegant shape and a light wood finish that looks great in any room. It is also easy to use and operate. I just need to fill the water tank, add a few drops of my favorite essential oil, and press the buttons on the front panel to choose the timer and the light mode.

        The diffuser has 4 timer settings: 1 hour, 3 hours, 6 hours, and continuous. I usually set it to 3 hours or continuous, depending on how long I want the diffuser to run. The diffuser also has an auto shut-off feature that turns it off when the water level is low, so I don't have to worry about it overheating or wasting electricity.

        The diffuser also has 7 ambient light modes that can create a relaxing and cozy atmosphere. The light can change colors automatically or stay in one color. I can also adjust the brightness and the intensity of the light by pressing the buttons on the side panel. The light is soft and soothing, and it does not disturb my sleep at night.

        The diffuser works well with any essential oil that I have tried. It produces a fine and even mist that spreads the aroma throughout the room. The aroma is not too strong or too weak, but just right. The diffuser also helps to humidify the air and improve the air quality. I feel more refreshed and relaxed when I use the diffuser.

        This diffuser also came with a starter pack of scents, so you can immediately plug in and go with this product without having to buy anything else.

        Color: Wood Grain + 10 Plant OilsVerified Purchase
        OBSERVATION:
        I wanted to purchase this product to add a fresh scent when I walked into the room. It provides a variety of scents, so I decided to purchase this.

        PROS:
        - I like that this product does not have any noise level. Compared to other diffusers, this product allows me to walk in my room without hearing any noise.

        - The product is easy to set up; simply plug the cord into the diffuser and add water until it reaches the maximum limit.

        CONS:
        - The essential oils that were provided have a faint scent. You cannot smell the essential oils (even when I put 20 drops). I thought that I was simply nose blind, but I put my personal essential oils into a new set of water and instantly smelled my essential oils.

        - The product feels cheap, and I am concerned it won't last long.

        OVERALL:
        - I wouldn't recommend purchasing this product if you're interested in a diffuser that will last long. If you're purchasing the diffuser because of the essential oils, I suggest purchasing another one and using your own oils.
